{"tid":818034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何輝話Now播埋歐聯","createTime":"2018-09-13T21:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T00:01:35.000Z","uid":8163,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca79710bfa5b0dce2c0b7362177a4ac1d23a23c2","tid":818034,"uid":8163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T21:10:11.000Z","msg":"【一台獨大】何輝直播爆料 「現在台」擸埋歐聯<br />\n<br />\n歐聯分組賽下周開鑼，正當全城關注香港直播權誰屬時，何輝今晚在《體蘋果》live節目【如何講英超】中突然爆料：「歐聯畀我做嗰個台攞埋喎。」另一主持何Wayne問邊個？何輝就話現在台。<br />\n<br />\n在香港睇歐聯直播，由09年起一直由有線取得獨家播映權，但近年該台多次傳出財困，所以去季後便結束連續9季的歐聯播映權。事實上，已擁有英超、西甲、意甲、德甲及法甲五大聯賽的Now TV，其中一條頻道beIN Sports，在上月尾(30號)已直播歐聯分組賽抽籤儀式，所以新一季歐聯落入Now TV平台亦算合理。據了解，Now TV將會在周五公佈有關消息，現卻被何輝在節目中無意間透露了。<br />\n<br />\n不過，另有消息指，beIN Sports亦有將部份歐聯播映權買了給有線，情況就與上季FOX將德甲播映權，分別賣給Now及有線一樣，兩台共同播一個聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180913/58679059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58679059&d=%2Bl2vR8Jhozw9xCS%2Bz2JLpNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4f7dc62c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58679059&h=d42d15c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180913/58679059</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個台都有得播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fa1e98ea734ab6efa87b38a00d62b24077bf3a","tid":818034,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"是唔是真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}